  "title": "Sales & Marketing Assistant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist with sales and marketing coordination activities</p></li><li><p>Communicate with potential clients via phone, WhatsApp, or email</p></li><li><p>Support basic marketing campaigns and outreach initiatives</p></li><li><p>Follow up with enquiries and maintain simple records</p></li><li><p>Work with the team to meet campaign or sales objectives</p></li><li><p>Perform administrative and reporting tasks related to sales activities</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Hiring only Singaporean/PR & Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate clearly in English</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with basic digital tools (WhatsApp, email, Google Docs)</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn and take initiative</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Sales or marketing experience is a plus, but not required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Monthly salary between <strong>SGD 2,900 – 4,000</strong> (based on experience & performance)</p></li><li><p>Structured training and support provided</p></li><li><p>Exposure to sales processes and digital marketing fundamentals</p></li><li><p>Performance-based incentives and growth opportunities</p></li><li><p>Supportive and collaborative team environment</p></li></ul>",
